{
  "stem": "753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The clerk came out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[SIGHS] He said, follow me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was this beautiful door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it looked to me majestic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then we entered that room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He closes the door behind us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the worst nightmare was sitting on the throne-- an SS officer with-- in a very elegant uniform.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] I don't know what kind of rank he had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't introduce himself to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he was looking at us, like, with these piercing eyes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think the fear of uniform I really never shed off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- even today, when a policeman stops me-- the most benevolent policeman-- I shake.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, of course, as befitted the master race, was even good-looking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was quite young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And behind him was a man standing in civil clothes, which I didn't know at that moment who he was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then I realized he was the interpreter who was supposed to interpret from German to Italian and back and forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I spoke quite well German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As you know, my maternal grandmother was Austrian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I made right away in my brain, like, a decision that I don't know German because German-- only refugees spoke and Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "An Italian-- a pure Italian speaks only Italian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he started questioning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The questions were long, [SIGHS] very precise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I always waited for the interpreter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I answered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Suddenly, in one moment, he said, ask her if she speaks German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was to confuse me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I waited, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] answered no.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
